            <div class="course-grid">
                <div class="course-content">
                    <div class="course-badge">Biostimulation</div>
                    <h2>Poly-L-Lactic Acid (PLLA) for Face & Body Rejuvenation Course</h2>
                    <p>This specialized 2-day biostimulatory training program focuses exclusively on the revolutionary collagen-stimulating treatment using Poly-L-Lactic Acid for comprehensive facial and body rejuvenation.</p>
                    
                    <div class="course-applications">
                        <div class="applications-title">
                            <i class="fas fa-body"></i>
                            Treatment Areas
                        </div>
                        <div class="applications-grid">
                            <div class="application-item">Facial Zones</div>
                            <div class="application-item">Neck & Décolleté</div>
                            <div class="application-item">Arms & Hands</div>
                            <div class="application-item">Abdomen</div>
